		<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><p><small> <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/0.8_(Romero)" title="0.8 (Romero)">‹———— 0.8</a> &#8195; <a href="/cdda_wiki/index.php/0.6_(Samedi)" title="0.6 (Samedi)">0.6 ————›</a> </small> <br />
<a class="mw-selflink selflink">0.7 (Lindqvist)</a> is a version of Cataclysm that was released on 2013 July 19.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
